#: ../../source/unit/ssr.rst:3 8d65ae01c2954b0f84d469298ee5e550
msgid "SSR Unit"
msgstr "SSR Unit"

#: ../../source/unit/ssr.rst:7 45dd3efb32004541843a808aa6b9f0c3
msgid ""
"UNIT SSR Solid-state relays are different from traditional "
"electromagnetic relays in that their switching life are much longer than "
"that of electromagnetic relays. With integrated MOC3043M optocoupler "
"isolation and zero-crossing detection,It supports input 3.3-5V DC control"
" signal, and control output single-phase 220-250V AC power."
msgstr ""
"UNIT SSR 固态继电器与传统电磁继电器不同，其开关寿命比电磁继电器长得多。它集成 MOC3043M 光耦隔离和过零检测，支持输入 "
"3.3-5V DC 控制信号，并控制输出单相 220-250V AC 电源。"

